invalid type: string "TOKYO - 5 DAYS:\nDay 1: Shinjuku, Meiji Shrine, Harajuku.\nDay 2: Senso-ji temple Asakusa, Akihabara electronics district.\nDay 3: TeamLab digital art, Odaiba, Tokyo Skytree.\nDay 4: Day trip to Nikko or Kamakura (giant Buddha).\nDay 5: Ginza shopping, Tsukiji fish market. Depart.\n\nDUBAI - 4 DAYS:\nDay 1: Burj Khalifa, Dubai Mall, Dubai Fountain show.\ndance. Depart.\n\nxpe